:

1. *Očima* je pregledao celu sobu. (He inspected the whole room with his eyes.)
2. Na njen *očima* su bile suze. (There were tears in her eyes.)
3. *Očima* su se sreli i zaljubili. (They met and fell in love with their eyes.)
4. On je celu ulicu pregledao *očima*. (He inspected the whole street with his eyes.)
5. Ona je na njega gledala *očima* punim ljubavi. (She looked at him with eyes full of love.)
6. *Očima* je pregledao knjigu. (He inspected the book with his eyes.)